  "title": "Electrical Engineer (Construction / Training Provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong in project execution from start to end of project cycle.</p></li><li><p>Exhibit site solving skill & site coordination to customer.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate, monitor & control of supplier's materials/equipment’s & subcontractors' installation quality.</p></li><li><p>Produce shop drawings & coordination of drawings etc.</p></li><li><p>Prepare work schedules & attend client meeting and internal meeting.</p></li><li><p>Understand control system philosophy for M&E Services</p></li><li><p>To assist manager/ project director on the day-to-day activities under the Master Planning schedule, Quality, safety, Etc.</p></li><li><p>Check for non-conformance product or installation to avoid defects.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in Electrical Engineering and relevant Building construction safety supervisor certificate or equivalent</p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website <a href=\"http://www.trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.trustrecruit.com.sg</a>.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Lee Jia Xiang</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25158171</p>",
